At PROTO IMAGES, we've been creating compelling advertising images for exhibit builders, the trade show industry, and other global companies for over 10 years. We specialize in a variety of photography styles and have a range of video services available for documenting conferences and corporate events, exhibits and booths, commercial and retail environments. Our additional areas of expertise include business headshots, green screen / photo booth, and on-site printing services. We are available for hire at all major trade shows and conferences across the US and worldwide.

